	<DIV CLASS="headlinestory"><B>Is the Middle East peace process dead?</B><BR></DIV>
	<FONT FACE="sans-serif" SIZE="2">
	
	
		
		<DIV CLASS="inlineimage">
		<IMG alt="" vspace="0" border=0 width="300" height="120" src="/web/20001203074700im_/http://news.bbc.co.uk/olmedia/965000/images/_969326_violence_tp300.jpg"><BR CLEAR="all">
		
		</DIV>
		
	
	



	
	
		
	





	<DIV CLASS="bodytext"><B>Can the Middle East peace process survive the unprecedented levels of violence between Israelis and Palestinians?
</B>
<P>
Weeks of chaos in Israel and the occupied territories have left hundreds dead, most of them Palestinians. Despite intense diplomatic efforts, the violence continues.
<P>
<B>Can there still be talk about a Middle East peace process? What can be done to restore calm? How can trust ever be rebuilt between the two sides after the ugly scenes of the past few days? </B>
<P>
<I>We discussed the crisis in the Middle East on Talking Point ON AIR.</I> 
<P>
