thousands of years!)  unless
 they change their mind-set.
<BR><B><I>
Regina Faria,
Santa Cruz, USA
</I></B><P> Having read many history books, past experiences counts.  For Israel, its just like having won a battle and lost the war!  There will never be peace in the region judging from the demands from both sides. No one is able to agree to each other's demand for political reason. Stone throwing Palestinians is not the whole picture! There are those with rifles as well and vice versa for the Israelis.
<BR><B><I>
Botak,
Singapore
